{"tid":1278516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[心靈雞湯] 重覺得冇未來、好絕望嘅入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:20:42.000Z","uid":75514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"baf5233cae2a4bd65af81b82f4a0ce6353694238","tid":1278516,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"如果重有人係覺得見唔到未來、好絕望嘅話，試下用咁嘅心態去睇件事：<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋<span style=\"color: red;\">擺明就係要個政府同政權跪低</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>個政權唔跪，就打斷佢對腳</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n個政府本來就應該係香港人嘅<br />\n本來就應該係香港人要你企就企，要你跪就跪<br />\n唔聽話嘅政府，比人拆祠堂都冇得怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人先自侮而後人侮之，既然香港政府唔理香港人嘅要求，咁就要搞到你香港政府賤過地底泥，行到邊衰到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會都係一樣<br />\n如果香港係一個國家，立法會就係國會，理應係民選組成<br />\n一個容許DQ存在嘅國會，成幢比人燒通頂都係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會容許警察進入國會範圍，比佢哋四處走嘅秘書處，全部決策者捉晒去剝衫遊街示眾都太便宜佢哋<br />\n今次香港人淨係爆入去讀個咁溫和嘅宣言，已經係好俾面<br />\n一個本來屬於人民嘅地方，人民走入去係天公地道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，而家唔單係純粹消極咁同個政權鬥長命，而係應該將癱瘓個政權變成我哋日常生活嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩殘而家呢個政權，要佢不得好死，係天經地義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持外國勢力介入呢啲更加唔洗講，任何有助打擊、削弱個政府嘅嘢都應該做多啲做快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一個殘廢嘅政府，就係一個好嘅獨裁政府</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家加油，繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f7871f101842eaaa9fecea899c5c0becbbb29e","tid":1278516,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d2681fffa66e354579fbfcf3ba5bc8921ba8f5","tid":1278516,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}